r"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-4YQ","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":843,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/06\/08\/cruel-not-enter-paradise\/","url_meta":{"origin":19148,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Cruelty: Harsh, mean people do not enter Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 8, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Harithah ibn Wahb reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNeither the haughty, nor the cruel, will enter Paradise.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 4801 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062d\u064e\u0627\u0631\u0650\u062b\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0647\u0652\u0628\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0627 \u064a\u064e\u062f\u0652\u062e\u064f\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062c\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0629\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35430,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/03\/27\/jannah-bi-ghayri-hisab\/","url_meta":{"origin":19148,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Tawakkul: Paradise without reckoning, they relied on Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 27, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Imran ibn Husayn reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSeventy thousand from my nation will enter Paradise without reckoning.\u201d They said, \u201cWho are they, O Messenger of Allah?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThey are those who do not rely on incantations, nor believe in omens, nor use\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33762,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/11\/13\/women-fully-clothed-naked\/","url_meta":{"origin":19148,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Seduction: Women who are fully-clothed, but naked","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 13, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Salih reported: Abu Huraira, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cSome women are clothed but naked, inclining to evil and seducing with it. They will not enter Paradise, nor smell its fragrance, even though it can be found from a distance of five hundred years of travel.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18089,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/02\/09\/three-not-enter-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":19148,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Sins: Three people will not enter Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 9, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThree persons will not be looked upon by Allah Almighty on the Day of Resurrection: one who disobeys his parents, a woman who imitates men, and a man who allows his women to fornicate. Three\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37460,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/11\/29\/jannah-made-of\/","url_meta":{"origin":19148,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Jannah: What is Paradise made out of?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 29, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: I said, \u201cWhat is Paradise built from?\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBricks of silver and gold, its mortar is musk of strong fragrance, its pebbles are pearls and rubies, and its soil is saffron. Whoever enters it will enjoy bliss\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":503,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/02\/08\/none-enters-paradise-by-deeds\/","url_meta":{"origin":19148,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Salvation: None enters Paradise by deeds alone","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 8, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"None of you will enter Paradise by his good deeds alone, nor would you be rescued from the Hellfire, not even myself, but for the mercy of Allah.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2817 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u064